 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  process  of  building  something .  Setting  up  framing ,  tr uss  and  beam  are  steps  in  building  a  structure .  New  construction  is  a  process  of  building  something  new ,  which  includes  setting  up  framing ,  tr uss  and  beam .  Warehouse  is  a  type  of  building ,  but  not  the  process  of  building .  Driving  is  not  related  to  building .  Ceiling  is  a  part  of  a  building ,  but  not  the  process  of  building .  Bridge  is  a  type  of  structure  that  requires  setting  up  framing ,  tr uss  and  beam .  So  the  answer  is  new  construction  ( a ).

